definition: to leave/to depart/to separate/to distinguish/to classify/other/another/don't ...!/to pin/to stick (sth) in
to make sb change their ways, opinions etc
of/~'s (possessive particle)/(used after an attribute)/(used to form a nominal expression)/(used at the end of a declarative sentence for emphasis)

sentences.english: No thanks, I would rather go somewhere else.
sentences.chinese: 那就算了，我再去别的地方看看吧。

sentences.english: 'I am, ' replied the Doger. 'I'd scorn to be anything else.
sentences.chinese: “是啊，”机灵鬼答道，“别的行当我还瞧不上呢。”

sentences.english: Doesn't paronychia cut fingernail to still have other treatment method?
sentences.chinese: 甲沟炎不切指甲还有别的治疗方法吗？

sentences.english: Then we Can achieve a fulfillment that no other living creature will ever know.
sentences.chinese: 那么我们就能取得别的生物所不能取得的满足感。

sentences.english: Don't let the devil convince you otherwise.
sentences.chinese: 不要让魔鬼用别的方式说服你。

sentences.english: However, this defeats the strong typing of the anonymous type.
sentences.chinese: 但是，这无法用于强型别的匿名型别。

sentences.english: Part of that revenue loss, however, would be recouped through other taxes.
sentences.chinese: 但是，这些税收的部分损失将从别的税种上补偿回来。

sentences.english: I see, but is there another method to figure out?
sentences.chinese: 我了解，但是否有别的办法可想呢？

sentences.english: No animal must ever kill any other animal.
sentences.chinese: 任何动物不得杀害别的动物。

sentences.english: The other students admired his depth of understanding.
sentences.chinese: 别的学生佩服他的理解力深刻。

sentences.english: Son of man KongZhu dream Dan by other seduce, woke up very worried.
sentences.chinese: 孙子梦到丹孔珠被别的男人勾引，醒来之后非常担忧。

sentences.english: Those whom God leaves out of selection he is also reproving, and for no other reason than that he wills to exclude them.
sentences.chinese: 上帝如果不拣选你，没有别的原因，他就是把你放逐。

sentences.english: We're already part of the U.N. and God knows what else.
sentences.chinese: 我们已经是联合国的成员了，天知道还有别的什么。

sentences.english: And blaspheming , many other things they said against him.
sentences.chinese: 他们还说了许多别的侮辱他的话。

sentences.english: I know no way of judging of the future but by the past.
sentences.chinese: 我深知，除了经历，决无别的可用来判断未来。

sentences.english: No extra money to go and buy other things.
sentences.chinese: 已经没有闲钱能用或者来买别的东西了。

definition: to say again/to put off a discussion until later/moreover/what's more/besides
anyway/in any case/to come over from the enemy's side
only natural/as it should be/certainly/of course/without doubt
dialectal equivalent of 什麼|什么[shen2 me5]/also pr. [sha4]
only/just (i.e. it is only that...)/all except/unique
